<DOCNO> AP890508-0032 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-05-08-89 0523EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>r i PM-RitualSlayings-Reax     05-08 0482</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Ritual Slayings-Reax,0497</SECOND>
<HEAD>Retransmits a0458 to fix slugline</HEAD>
<HEAD>Cult Leader's Death, Arrests Bring Some Relief on Border</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Ritual Slayings, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOEL WILLIAMS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
