<HEAD>Guerrilla Kills Girlfriend, Turns Gun on Himself</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LUSAKA, Zambia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An African National Congress guerrilla
shot and killed his girlfriend, then turned the gun on himself,
police said Monday.
   Neighbors in the capital's Mtendere suburb reported Sunday they
heard the shooting, which evidently followed a domestic dispute,
said Police Chief Zunga Siakalima.
