higher with the contract for delivery in May at $4.38{ a bushel;
corn was unchanged to 1{ cents lower with May at $2.80{ a bushel;
oats were 1\ cents to 3\ cents lower with May at $1.94{ a bushel;
soybeans were 5} cents lower to 3{ cents higher with May at $7.63 a
bushel.
